    • Field Detail

      • access

        private java.lang.String access
        The level of privacy for this user story. It can be private or public. Private: only the owner can view the user story Public: everyone can view the user story

      • creationDate

        private java.util.Date creationDate
        The date when the user story has been created

      • dataElements

        private java.util.List<DataElement> dataElements
        The list of data elements contained in the user story

      • id

        private int id
        The unique ID of the user story

      • mode

        private java.lang.String mode
        The mode of the user story. It can be 'active', 'passive' or 'published'. Active: there is only one active user story per user, it is considered as its 'Workboard'. The user can add and remove data elements form the user story. Passive: the user story is being edited by the user Published: nothing can be modified by the user as the story is published.

      • name

        private java.lang.String name
        The name of the user story

      • owner

        private User owner
        The user who created the user story

      • publishDate

        private java.util.Date publishDate
        The date when the user story has been published

      • purpose

        private java.lang.String purpose
        The purpose of the user story

      • seaport

        private Seaport seaport
        The seaport to which the user story is related

        private static final long serialVersionUID
